Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.45,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Good morning, Lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.84,0:00:03.83,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Good morning, Toko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.83,0:00:05.91,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Have you seen anything since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:09.49,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,No, I haven’t. Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.87,0:00:11.16,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Have you heard anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.64,0:00:15.30,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Sometimes I hear something very confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:20.15,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Very confused? One person? More than one?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.55,0:00:24.77,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,More than one. Men and women.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.77,0:00:26.77,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Are they people you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.77,0:00:28.62,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.02,0:00:34.20,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,You said that you heard things from the sky. What do you think is in the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.76,0:00:36.64,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,There’s air.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:38.84,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Uh, huh. And aside from that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.29,0:00:43.35,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Clouds. The sun. The stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:46.90,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Do you know about the transmission of radio wavelengths for TV and cell phones?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.30,0:00:50.48,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Yes. The information travels wirelessly?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:52.96,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Right. The information flies through the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.89,0:00:56.70,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Am I hearing that information?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.70,0:01:02.01,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Hmm. It might be that you imagine you are hearing that information.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.01,0:01:04.17,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,There’s a sickness like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:05.94,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,There is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.36,0:01:07.94,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,It’s called delusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:12.80,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,It’s a symptom of schizophrenia and neurosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.80,0:01:18.41,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Sometimes, if you are focusing much too much on something or are getting very stressed, it can bring out those kind of symptoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.79,0:01:19.55,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:20.63,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:25.52,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Usually, when people say they hear things, what they hear is more closely associated with themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.05,0:01:28.70,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,For instance, they hear voices that bad-mouth them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.25,0:01:30.57,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Delusion of persecution?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.57,0:01:31.36,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:34.47,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,You’ve been studying up on this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:38.73,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Ok. I’ll fill you in a little more on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.44,0:01:54.15,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,The definition of “delusion” is taking a mistaken idea and believing in your own mind that it is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:02:00.02,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,But for you, Lain, you say that you might have felt or sensed something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:03.68,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,A person who is really delusional tends to have conviction that his delusions are real.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,But you don’t have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:07.20,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,You have thoughts, considerations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:08.44,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Considerations?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:11.88,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,You can forget that word if you’d like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.80,0:02:18.88,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,As I mentioned before, a delusion is generally something intertwined with one’s self.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:21.97,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,There really aren’t any delusions that have nothing to do with someone personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.97,0:02:23.44,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I’m not delusional?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.44,0:02:25.28,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Fundamentally, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.28,0:02:33.04,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Still, there are all sorts of delusions, and if you try to “pin” one of them onto someone, you may start pinning other ones on that person, too.
